        <mxCell id="sbMdM6gBOHIMnYuIiBfh-2" value="&lt;pre style=&quot;overflow-x: auto; white-space: pre; box-sizing: border-box; border-radius: 4px; max-width: 100%; margin: 0px; padding: 8px; color: rgb(191, 191, 191); font-size: 13px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(25, 26, 27); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;font-family: monospace; color: rgb(140, 140, 140); background-color: rgb(38, 38, 38); padding: 0px; border-radius: 3px; word-break: break-word; font-size: 0.9em;&quot;&gt;┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐&#xa;│                    SERVER (Authority)                            │&#xa;│                                                                  │&#xa;│  ATDGameMode                                                     │&#xa;│  ├── UTDWaveManagerComponent      ← 웨이브 진행, Enemy 추적     │&#xa;│  ├── UTDEnemySpawnerComponent     ← Enemy 스폰 (서버 전용)       │&#xa;│  ├── UTDTowerSpawnerComponent     ← Tower 스폰 (서버 전용)       │&#xa;│  └── UTDPoolComponent             ← Projectile 풀링             │&#xa;│                                                                  │&#xa;│  ATDGameState (Replicated)                                       │&#xa;│  ├── Coins                        ← 복제됨, OnCoinsChanged       │&#xa;│  └── 게임 진행 상태                                              │&#xa;│                                                                  │&#xa;└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘&#xa;                            ║&#xa;                            ║ Replication / RPC&#xa;                            ║&#xa;┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐&#xa;│                   CLIENT (LocalPlayer)                           │&#xa;│                                                                  │&#xa;│  ATDPlayerController (입력 + UI Lifecycle)                       │&#xa;│  ├── HandleClick                  ← Enhanced Input               │&#xa;│  ├── ShowTowerActionMenu          ← Widget 생성/표시             │&#xa;│  └── Server_DoTowerAction (RPC)   ← 단일 진입점                  │&#xa;│                                                                  │&#xa;│  UTDTowerActionWidgetBase (UI Logic)                             │&#xa;│  └── WBP_TowerActions (UI Visual)                                │&#xa;│                                                                  │&#xa;└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" vertex="1" parent="1">
